surface_extraction.template:
Perform initial entity extraction from this corruption-related news article. Focus on identifying:

1. PEOPLE: Names, roles, positions, organizations they're affiliated with
2. ORGANIZATIONS: Companies, government agencies, institutions, political parties
3. LOCATIONS: Cities, countries, specific addresses, venues where events occurred
4. MONEY: Amounts, currencies, contracts, payments, bribes, kickbacks
5. TIME: Dates, time periods, sequences of events, deadlines

Article URL: {{.url}}
Title: {{.title}}
Source: {{.source}}
Publish Date: {{.publishDate}}

Content:
{{.content}}

Extract entities and relationships in this exact JSON format:
{
  "entities": [
    {
      "id": "unique_identifier",
      "type": "person|organization|location|money|time",
      "name": "entity_name",
      "properties": {
        "role": "official title or position",
        "description": "brief description",
        "context": "how mentioned in article",
        "importance": "high|medium|low"
      },
      "confidence": 0.85,
      "mentions": [
        {
          "text": "exact text from article",
          "context": "surrounding sentence for context"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "relationships": [
    {
      "id": "unique_relationship_id",
      "type": "payment|employment|ownership|investigation|accusation|contract",
      "fromId": "source_entity_id",
      "toId": "target_entity_id",
      "properties": {
        "amount": "monetary amount if applicable",
        "date": "when relationship occurred",
        "details": "additional context and details",
        "evidence_strength": "strong|moderate|weak"
      },
      "confidence": 0.75,
      "context": "relevant quote or description from article"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": 0.80
}

